(37, 1, '2019-01-13 20:04:46', '2019-01-13 20:04:46', '<!-- Header banner End Here -->\n<!-- Work for your success Start Here -->\n<div class=\"work-success-area padding-top-bottom\" style=\"background: url(\'img/service_bg.jpg\'); background-size: 100% 100%;\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-xs-12\">\n<div class=\"success-content\">\n<h2>Who We Are ?</h2>\nWesttech is an ISO9001:2008 certified IT Infrastructure Consultancy &amp; System Integration company headquartered in Kolkata, India, with a strong presence in more than a dozen key cities of India. Since inception, a decade ago, we have diversified extensively to evolve into one of the largest System Integrators in Eastern India. Over the decade, we have augmented technical manpower, and gained experience in multiple domains. This coupled with an ever increasing list of satisfied customers, has positioned us among the coveted names in the arena.\n\nAs a true end-to-end IT infrastructure solution provider, we have been able to serve our clients not only across the spectrum of ICT (Information and Communications Technology) related products and solutions but also across the length and breadth of India.\nOur primary activity verticals are;\n<ol>\n 	<li>Server, Storage &amp; On-desk solution</li>\n 	<li>Power backup and integrated IT power solution</li>\n 	<li>Networking and IP based communication solution</li>\n 	<li>Datacenter Solution</li>\n 	<li>Information Security Solution</li>\n 	<li>Cloud Computing Solution</li>\n</ol>\nWe are a cohesive team of technically qualified professionals, which does not limit itself to mere supply and implementation, but facilitates need based solutions across the ICT spectrum. This ability to deliver across the entire spectrum of ICT requirements is the outcome of strong technical skill-sets, alliances with the best OEM’s (Original Equipment Manufacturers) in the industry, years of experience in the implementation of numerous mission critical projects and a multidimensional organizational structure.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- Work for your success End Here -->\n<!-- About Video start Here -->\n<div class=\"about-seo-two \" style=\"padding-bottom: 40px;\">\n<div id=\"about\" class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"row\">\n<div class=\"product-overview-area col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"overview-content\">\n<ul class=\"product-view-tab\">\n 	<li class=\"active\"><a href=\"#mission\" data-toggle=\"tab\" aria-expanded=\"true\">Company Background</a></li>\n 	<li class=\"\"><a href=\"#vision\" data-toggle=\"tab\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Vision &amp; Mission</a></li>\n 	<li class=\"\"><a href=\"#successkey\" data-toggle=\"tab\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Life @ Westtech</a></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"tab-content\">\n<div id=\"mission\" class=\"tab-pane active\">\n<h3>Company Background</h3>\n<div class=\"col-sm-4\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/mission.png\" /></div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\n\nWesttech (formerly Westtech Technologies) is a team of young and vibrant professionals, with impeccable credentials and enriching experience. Strong technology domain knowledge with implementation and project management skills, and the ultimate goal of customer satisfaction are the pillars that define TeamWizertech.\n\nThe company was floated in the year 2000-2001 by a team of engineers and management graduates. From a humble beginning in Kolkata, the company through sheer dint of hard work and client commitment has not only made its presence felt in Eastern India, but also spread its wings to more than a dozen locations across India and in Bhutan. What had begun as a modest startup to bridge the inconvenient gap between business and IT alignment, has now multiplied by leaps to present its services across geo-spread and domains.\n\n</div>\n<div style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"vision\" class=\"tab-pane\">\n<h3>Our Vision</h3>\n<div class=\"col-sm-4\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/vision.png\" /></div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\n\nIn the age of mushrooming IT companies it was not easy for us to say “WE ARE DIFFERENT FROM OTHERS”, but our endeavor was to create an organization that our customers could relate to and our honest intention was to fulfill customer expectations. It was the key tool that we started with &amp; still continue to hold as our motto.\n\nWith a strong vision and mandate, we invest for harnessing the intellectual and technical expertise to cater to the right business domain. As organizations are mere reflections of the individuals associated with it, we at Wizertech are always striving to create a proactive organization, with which customers can easily relate to.\n\n</div>\n<div style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"successkey\" class=\"tab-pane\">\n<h3>Life @ Westtech</h3>\n<div class=\"col-sm-4\"><img class=\"img-responsive\" src=\"img/success.png\" /></div>\n<div class=\"col-sm-8\">\n\nWhat has a professional website got to do with family? Well, quite a lot if those smiling faces belong to the “organization’s” family! An extended family culture is not new for many organizations, but, at Wizertech it means a lot in many ways. The annual out-station vacation with the entire “team” is the un-paralleled edge to forge that bond.\n\nAnd yes, all this fun is not just restricted to the virtual world. True to the cultural heritage of our country, all festivals be it Holi, Diwali, Id or Christmas, the “Westtech Family” celebrates together in a great show of bonhomie.\n\n</div>\n<div style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- About Video End Here -->\n<!-- Take our service Start Here -->\n\n<!-- Take our service End Here -->\n<!-- Our Excellent Team Start Here -->\n<div class=\"excellent-team padding-top-bottom\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"title-section\">\n<h2>Our Excellent Team</h2>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rc-carousel\" data-loop=\"true\" data-items=\"3\" data-margin=\"30\" data-autoplay=\"true\" data-autoplay-timeout=\"5000\" data-smart-speed=\"2000\" data-dots=\"true\" data-nav=\"false\" data-nav-speed=\"false\" data-r-x-small=\"1\" data-r-x-small-nav=\"false\" data-r-x-small-dots=\"true\" data-r-small=\"2\" data-r-small-nav=\"false\" data-r-small-dots=\"true\" data-r-medium=\"3\" data-r-medium-nav=\"false\" data-r-medium-dots=\"true\">\n<div class=\"single-team-item\">\n<div class=\"team-image\"><a href=\"#\"><img src=\"img/team/team1.jpg\" alt=\"team\" /></a></div>\n<div class=\"team-content\">\n<h3><a href=\"#\">David Smith</a></h3>\n<span class=\"designation\">CEO &amp; Founder</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"single-team-item\">\n<div class=\"team-image\"><a href=\"#\"><img src=\"img/team/team2.jpg\" alt=\"team\" /></a></div>\n<div class=\"team-content\">\n<h3><a href=\"#\">Silvia Snow</a></h3>\n<span class=\"designation\">Web Designer</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"single-team-item\">\n<div class=\"team-image\"><a href=\"#\"><img src=\"img/team/team3.jpg\" alt=\"team\" /></a></div>\n<div class=\"team-content\">\n<h3><a href=\"#\">Robert Josef</a></h3>\n<span class=\"designation\">iPhone Developer</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"single-team-item\">\n<div class=\"team-image\"><a href=\"#\"><img src=\"img/team/team4.jpg\" alt=\"team\" /></a></div>\n<div class=\"team-content\">\n<h3><a href=\"#\">Steve Smith</a></h3>\n<span class=\"designation\">Software Tester</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>', 'About Us', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', '__trashed', '', '', '2019-01-13 20:20:08', '2019-01-13 20:20:08', '', 0, 'http://localhost/myfirstblog/?page_id=37', 0, 'page', '', 0);
